how do i get my kitten to love me i know it sounds like a really wierd question but i've never had a cat before i want this one to love me and trust me but how treat it kindly feed it regularly or times a day make sure it's always got fresh water to drink play with it with wool feathers bits of paper anything that makes a rustling noise take it to the vet whenever it's ill let it sleep when it's tired cats need to sleep about hours a day provide a blanket or something warm for it to sleep on in a quiet part of the house my cats have my old dressing gowns to sleep on don't handle the kitten roughly always make sure the back legs are supported look at books from the library or websites about how to care for your cat treat the cat with care and respect and it will reward you with years of affection Fancy rat Mattress Guinea pig Cat Japanese tea ceremony Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Insomnia Characters in the Smurfs Chicken Sleep Looney Tunes and Merrie Melodies filmography Feral cat Phoebe Buffay's songs Pitaten Pet skunk Little Britain Hamster Shaggy dog story Sleeping bag The Care Bears Adventure in Wonderland Mojave people Andy Warhol The Lion, the Witch and the Wardrobe Ferret Garfield Customs and etiquette of Japan Cats (musical) Dean Koontz A Day in the Life First aid Kitten Purr Comanche Friends Fruits Basket Dairy Animal rights Humphrey Bogart Urinary incontinence Manx (cat) Gramophone record Yami to B__shi to Hon no Tabibito Social rule Basic English The Beatles bootlegs Joy Division (band) Trailer Park Boys Socialization Rod McKuen Euphemism Ron and Fez Turkish Van Capercaillie Care Bears Hafler Trio Wound Placebo (band) Housebreaking Flea Theory of conduct The Beatles Burglary Zagreus (Doctor Who audio) Badly Drawn Kitties Thermoregulation Cat o' nine tails Hiking Characters of The Sandman Dog Dr. Seuss Oasis (band) Prostate cancer Pet Cocaine Non-Hodgkin's lymphoma Blankets (graphic novel) Fecal incontinence Atomic Kitten Saga (band) Gormenghast "Weird Al" Y